1
00:00:02,510 --> 00:00:06,150
[After her date with Eunchae...]

2
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:12,530
[She stands there for a while,
sending someone a message on SBM Talk]

3
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:15,300
I wonder how this will end up.

4
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:17,570
[Jinwoo: Wait, did you hear something just now?]

5
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,870
[Seungho: Should I check it out, just in case?]

6
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:23,310
[Hyeyeon: How was the date? I'm back at the beach.
I'll tell you everything later.]

7
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:25,470
[Jinwoo: You didn't get anything, did you?]

8
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:25,230
I did. I did.

9
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:28,640
[Seungho: I got an SBM Talk notification.]
[Jinwoo: Oh, really?]

10
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:31,040
[Seungho: But we're on a date.]

11
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,700
[Seungho: I'll reply later.]

12
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,520
[Jinwoo: That hurts.]

13
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:40,660
[A text from a rival mid-date.
What happens next?]

14
00:00:46,290 --> 00:00:51,130
[After their first meeting and the Secret Room,
this is their third date]

15
00:00:52,270 --> 00:00:55,610
[Total silence]

16
00:00:57,710 --> 00:00:58,520
[Hahaha]

17
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:01,200
[Seungho: Why are you so quiet?]

18
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:04,620
[Jinwoo: No, it's just...]

19
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:09,320
[Seungho: Jinwoo is usually so lively.]

20
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:12,470
[Seungho: He talks the most
when we're all together.]

21
00:01:12,470 --> 00:01:15,560
[Seungho: But when it's just the two of us,]

22
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,210
[Seungho: he becomes much quieter.]

23
00:01:17,510 --> 00:01:18,750
[Jinwoo: Being alone in the car together]

24
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:21,370
[Jinwoo: on the way to our date]

25
00:01:21,370 --> 00:01:22,710
[Jinwoo: felt completely different.]

26
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:24,270
[Jinwoo: I was a bit shy.]

27
00:01:25,730 --> 00:01:28,280
[Jinwoo: My heart was actually racing a little.]

28
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:32,479
[Jinwoo: How do you feel
about going out with me?]

29
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:33,240
[Seungho: Mmh...]

30
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:35,060
[Seungho: Mmh... it's great!]

31
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:34,880
-Really? -Yeah.

32
00:01:36,979 --> 00:01:40,270
[Jinwoo: Same here. I'm having a great time.]

33
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,759
[Fidgeting]

34
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,380
[Cute] [Turn head]

35
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:50,860
[Seungho avoids eye contact]

36
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:53,000
[Seungho: That must be so fun.]

37
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,890
[Jinwoo: Where did that come from?]

38
00:01:54,130 --> 00:01:55,640
[Seungho: My mind just jumps around a lot.]

39
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,990
[Jinwoo: You just say whatever pops into your head?]

40
00:01:56,990 --> 00:01:58,600
[Seungho: Doesn't everyone?]

41
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,870
[Jinwoo: I used to be like that.]
[Seungho: Right?]

42
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:01,230
[Jinwoo: Mine probably jumps around even more.]
[Seungho: I know.]

43
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:05,330
[Seungho: I noticed that on day one.]
[Jinwoo: Ah, right.]

44
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:08,050
[Leaning over]

45
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:11,450
[Seungho: You can see how much time is left
until we get there.]

46
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,230
[Touch]

47
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:18,380
[Seungho naturally rests his hand
on Jinwoo's thigh]

48
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:20,800
1:00? I can't really see. The first digit is a 2.

49
00:02:21,070 --> 00:02:22,450
[Jinwoo: 2:03?]

50
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:24,240
[Jinwoo: Ah, 1:23.]

51
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:27,030
[Checking the time]

52
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,670
[Jinwoo: We're almost there.]

53
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:30,030
[Seungho: We still have some time.]

54
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:31,020
[Glance]

55
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:32,900
[Shy]

56
00:02:38,570 --> 00:02:40,790
[Seungho: I got a couple bracelet yesterday.]

57
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:41,970
[Jinwoo: I saw it.]

58
00:02:41,970 --> 00:02:44,540
[Jinwoo: You're only telling me this now, though.]

59
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:47,740
[Seungho: It didn't seem like you noticed.]

60
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:50,090
[Jinwoo: It's not that I didn't notice.]

61
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:52,220
[Jinwoo can't stop staring at the bracelet]

62
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:53,870
[Seungho: What do you think?]

63
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:55,700
[Seungho: Not a fan?]

64
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:58,550
[Jinwoo: Honestly, I don't feel great about it.]

65
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:02,100
[Jinwoo: But it's not even about feeling bad.]

66
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:03,610
[Jinwoo: It's just...]

67
00:03:03,610 --> 00:03:06,390
[Jinwoo: I guess I'm a little jealous.]

68
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:10,600
[Jinwoo: But you knew I'd get jealous.]

69
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,530
[Jinwoo: There's no way you didn't know.]

70
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:15,250
[Staring]

71
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:20,110
[Seungho just smiles without answering]

72
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,090
[Jinwoo: You should just
get matching bracelets with me too.]

73
00:03:23,090 --> 00:03:26,030
[Jinwoo: I don't really care that much.]

74
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:26,940
[Seungho: Really?]

75
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,740
[Seungho: Hyeyeon also put it on me.]

76
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:30,620
[Jinwoo: The band-aid?]

77
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,590
[Seungho: Yeah.
She even put some ointment on it earlier.]

78
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:37,570
[Jinwoo forces a smile]

79
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:41,610
[Seungho: But that's only because I got hurt
when we went out yesterday.]

80
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:43,040
[Jinwoo: Didn't you ask her to put it on you?]

81
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,120
-Not really. -No?

82
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,250
[Seungho: Not really.]

83
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:48,970
[Jinwoo: You keep making me jealous on purpose.]

84
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,150
[Seungho: What's wrong?]

85
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:51,820
[Seungho: Was that bad?]

86
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:52,290
[Seungho: Should I stop doing that?]

87
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:53,290
-Should I stop doing that? -No, no.

88
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:53,840
[Jinwoo: No, no.]

89
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,620
[Jinwoo: Do you like it
when people get jealous over you?]

90
00:03:57,079 --> 00:04:00,270
[Seungho: It's better than nothing, right?]

91
00:04:00,970 --> 00:04:02,570
[Jinwoo: True.]

92
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,540
[Jinwoo: But don't do it too often.]

93
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,960
[Jinwoo: Making me jealous on purpose.]

94
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,170
[Jinwoo: Got it?]

95
00:04:10,230 --> 00:04:12,230
[Seungho: Why?]

96
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:16,550
[Jinwoo: If you do it too much, it really hurts.]

97
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:19,660
[Jinwoo: I'd be lying if I said I didn't care.]

98
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:21,440
[Jinwoo: But I...]

99
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:24,480
[Jinwoo: will try my best not to show it.]

100
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:27,750
[Jinwoo: I won't interfere]

101
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,960
[Jinwoo: or get in their way.]

102
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:35,380
[Jinwoo: It's so windy.
It feels just like the place where we first met.]

103
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:35,650
Dejavu.

104
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:39,310
The wind is a bit calmer than it was back then.

105
00:04:39,570 --> 00:04:40,970
Are we making something?

106
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:48,500
[All kinds of ceramic ornaments]

107
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,890
[The pottery studio smells like coffee and fresh clay]

108
00:04:51,890 --> 00:04:54,790
[Gather & Create Studio]
[The pottery studio smells like coffee and fresh clay]

109
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:58,210
[Jinwoo: Whoa!]

110
00:04:58,710 --> 00:04:59,710
[Seungho: What are we doing here?]

111
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,570
[Jinwoo: This is amazing.]

112
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:07,340
[Jinwoo: I've never been to a place like this.]

113
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:10,210
[Seungho: Should we open it up?]
[Jinwoo: Okay.]

114
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:15,040
[Seungho: It's raw clay.]

115
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,470
[Jinwoo: Are we making it together?]

116
00:05:17,470 --> 00:05:19,500
[Jinwoo: I knew it was a pottery studio,]

117
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:23,090
[Jinwoo: but I thought we'd each
make our own thing.]

118
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:25,160
[Jinwoo: Then I saw that huge pottery wheel.]

119
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,140
[Jinwoo: Immediately, I knew]

120
00:05:26,140 --> 00:05:29,180
[Jinwoo: we would use our hands]

121
00:05:29,450 --> 00:05:32,130
["to naturally touch each other."]

122
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:35,690
[Seungho: I had absolutely no clue what to do.]

123
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:37,260
[Seungho: I was a bit worried.]

124
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:39,940
[Seungho: But I figured Jinwoo would help me out.]

125
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:43,420
[Seungho: So I wasn't too worried.]

126
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,090
[Seungho: Wow, this is so cool.]

127
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:46,170
Right?

128
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:48,140
[Jinwoo: Want to give it a try?]
[Alright.]

129
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,750
[Seungho: If I press like this, it gets narrower.]

130
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:54,340
[Seungho: How do I make it wider?]

131
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,880
-Like this, shape your hands like this. -Okay.

132
00:05:59,150 --> 00:06:00,830
[Jinwoo: Hold it like this and let it spin.]

133
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:03,090
[Jinwoo: It'll widen up, just like this.]

134
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:05,770
Put two fingers in, maybe three.

135
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:11,490
[Under Jinwoo's guidance,
their hands naturally wrap around each other]

136
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,910
[Seungho: How is it?]

137
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:14,660
[Jinwoo: Not bad.]

138
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:17,000
[Seungho: Really?]
[Jinwoo: Yeah.]

139
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:22,160
[Before they know it,
the vibe becomes completely relaxed]

140
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,660
[Seungho: This feels harder than surfing.]

141
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,070
[Jinwoo: Seriously?]

142
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,860
[Jinwoo: So you're doing something even harder
than surfing with me?]
[Seungho: Oh, I guess so.]

143
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,760
[Seungho: This is pretty special.]
[Jinwoo: Very special?]

144
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,510
[Jinwoo: Didn't you say yesterday
was the most exhausting?]

145
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:36,800
[Seungho: It was fun, but so hard.]

146
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,280
[Bump]

147
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:44,980
[Jinwoo: Oh, you okay?]
[Seungho: No.]

148
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:47,420
[Teasing each other with childish jokes
out of nowhere]

149
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:49,890
[Smearing clay]

150
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:51,420
[Smearing clay]
[Jinwoo: What are you doing?]

151
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:57,020
[Jinwoo: My bad. It keeps getting bulkier.]

152
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,659
[Seungho: Let me try.]

153
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:00,980
["Hold this for me."]

154
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:08,370
[Two pairs of hands on the clay, looking like one.]

155
00:07:04,610 --> 00:07:05,900
-This side is a bit... -This side?

156
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:07,190
Let me touch it up a bit.

157
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,320
It's honestly turning into a rice bowl.

158
00:07:12,250 --> 00:07:14,520
[Seungho: Yesterday, during my date with Hyeyeon,]

159
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,810
[Seungho: we had some natural skinship.]

160
00:07:16,810 --> 00:07:20,740
[Seungho: And Jinwoo and I had
the same kind of physical contact today.]

161
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:24,750
[Seungho: Oh, they were actually pretty similar
in that way.]

162
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:27,580
[Seungho: My heart did flutter a bit
during those moments.]

163
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:29,800
[Jinwoo: We touched a lot today.]

164
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,390
[Jinwoo: It made my heart race a bit.]

165
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:34,030
[Jinwoo: This date]

166
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:36,330
[Jinwoo: made me realize
my feelings all over again.]

167
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,580
[Jinwoo: Should we make it smaller?]
[Seungho: No.]

168
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:40,909
[Jinwoo: You sure?]
[Seungho: Yeah.]

169
00:07:40,909 --> 00:07:42,590
[Seungho: Actually, wait. Maybe a bit smaller...]

170
00:07:42,590 --> 00:07:43,310
[Jinwoo: Can I?]

171
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,310
[Seungho: I don't even know anymore.]

172
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:47,550
[Jinwoo: Just do whatever you want.]

173
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:45,390
No.

174
00:07:48,850 --> 00:07:51,380
["I don't know what I want."]

175
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:53,450
[Jinwoo: Ah, really?]

176
00:07:55,730 --> 00:07:58,000
[Seungho: Maybe I just get confused sometimes.]

177
00:07:58,930 --> 00:08:00,440
[Jinwoo: Like right now?]

178
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:00,400
Yeah.

179
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,080
[Seungho: The clay was the same way.]

180
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,830
[Jinwoo: The clay was like that...
Are other things the same way?

181
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:08,870
[A meaningful conversation]

182
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,020
[Jinwoo: How is it?]

183
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:13,620
[Seungho: I'm pretty happy with it.]

184
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:13,500
Happy?

185
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,320
[Seungho: What?]

186
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,360
[Jinwoo: Oh, I really like it.]
[Seungho: Right?]

187
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,880
[Seungho: Like who... or what?]

188
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:22,740
[Jinwoo: Everything... everything about it.]

189
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:25,270
[Shy]

190
00:08:26,930 --> 00:08:30,100
[Seungho:Let's just touch it up a little more.]
[Jinwoo: Then, wrap it up?]

191
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:31,510
[Seungho: Wrap it up?]
[Jinwoo: Sounds good.]

192
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,659
[Use this.]

193
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:33,350
This?

194
00:08:34,370 --> 00:08:35,750
[Seungho: Should I stop the wheel?]

195
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,450
Wait, wait!

196
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,230
Oh no.

197
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:50,160
[Seungho looks completely horrified]

198
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,800
-Give it to me. -What did you just do?

199
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,730
I'm so sorry.

200
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:49,940
Hold on.

201
00:08:50,370 --> 00:08:51,700
Is this still salvageable?

202
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:53,180
[Jinwoo is cracking up completely]

203
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,710
Probably not.

204
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,760
[Jinwoo: Right at the end when I was cutting it,]

205
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:59,770
[Jinwoo: the wire got tangled,
and the clay ended up like this.]

206
00:08:59,770 --> 00:09:00,930
[Jinwoo: It literally twisted into a pretzel.]

207
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:02,870
[Jinwoo: So it was a bit...]

208
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:04,050
[Jinwoo: I panicked a little,]

209
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:06,490
[Jinwoo: but it actually had a lot of character.]

210
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:08,810
[Jinwoo: It was a piece of art.]

211
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:15,870
[Their unique masterpiece is finished]

212
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:18,430
[Yongkyu: Want to sit down for a bit?]

213
00:09:18,430 --> 00:09:20,060
[Chaebe: Sure.]

214
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:28,510
[Yongkyu: We're already soaked.]

215
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,560
[Yongkyu: What else can we do...]

216
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,620
[Chaebe: This is nice, right?]
[Yongkyu: It's warm, isn't it?]

217
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:35,950
[Chaebe: Not bad.]
[Yongkyu: It's getting warmer.]

218
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:39,340
[Yongkyu: Have you ever hung out like this?]

219
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:40,320
[Shake head]

220
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,510
[Shake head]
[Yongkyu: Never?]
[Chaebe: Nope.]

221
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,900
[Yongkyu: Me neither.]

222
00:09:43,650 --> 00:09:46,420
[Yongkyu: Before getting into the water,]

223
00:09:46,610 --> 00:09:49,990
[Yongkyu: I usually think about]

224
00:09:49,990 --> 00:09:52,300
[Yongkyu: how uncomfortable it feels]

225
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:54,040
[Yongkyu: when wet clothes stick to you.]

226
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,370
[Yongkyu: In the past,]

227
00:09:55,370 --> 00:09:56,480
[Yongkyu: I would've just skipped it entirely.]

228
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:59,580
[Chaebe: It was really fun.]
[Yongkyu: Like you thought it was a wall,]

229
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:03,110
[Yongkyu: but it turned out to be a door.]

230
00:10:03,490 --> 00:10:06,130
[Yongkyu: I got to try something new.]

231
00:10:06,130 --> 00:10:09,190
[Yongkyu: Wow, these waves are...]

232
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:12,730
[Yeah, the ocean is beautiful.]

233
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,610
Yeah.

234
00:10:13,090 --> 00:10:14,380
[Thinking]

235
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:16,420
[Chaebe: Do you like people who act cute?]

236
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:20,120
[Yongkyu: Someone who acts cute?]
[Chaebe: Someone who expresses their feelings well.]

237
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,140
Expressive.

238
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:23,090
[Yongkyu: Of course, it's great
when someone does that.]

239
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:23,180
Right?

240
00:10:23,090 --> 00:10:24,870
[Yongkyu: Expressive people are great.]

241
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:27,170
[Yongkyu: My type has actually changed.]

242
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:32,730
[Yongkyu: I used to love puppy-like people.]

243
00:10:32,730 --> 00:10:35,000
[Yongkyu: Someone who always reaches out first,]

244
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:38,240
[Yongkyu: talks to me,]

245
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,960
[Yongkyu: and acts cute around me.]

246
00:10:40,290 --> 00:10:43,490
[Yongkyu: As I got older]

247
00:10:43,490 --> 00:10:46,760
[Yongkyu: and dated different people,]

248
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:49,980
[Yongkyu: I started liking]

249
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:52,080
[Yongkyu: people with more
of a cat-like personality, too.]

250
00:10:53,130 --> 00:10:55,160
[Chaebe: What type are you then?]

251
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,040
[Yongkyu: Me?]

252
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:57,820
[Yongkyu: I'm probably more of a cat.]

253
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:59,740
[Chaebe: A cat?]
[Yongkyu: Yeah.]

254
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:03,100
[Chaebe: So you don't really
express your feelings much?]

255
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:06,020
[Yongkyu: I used to be very expressive.]

256
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:09,470
[Yongkyu: But I've changed a lot.]

257
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:09,670
-Really? -Yeah.

258
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:13,310
[Chaebe: So,]

259
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:17,220
[Chaebe: you're attracted to people]

260
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:19,830
[Chaebe: who are like you?]

261
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,500
-Before. -I guess that's true.

262
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:23,650
[Yongkyu: Yeah, I guess that's true.]

263
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:22,350
Right?

264
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:28,060
[Yongkyu: I guess my preferences became broader.]

265
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:31,080
[Yongkyu: What about you?]

266
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:35,850
[Chaebe: I definitely prefer expressive people.]

267
00:11:35,850 --> 00:11:39,450
[Chaebe: That's the only way I feel loved.]

268
00:11:39,450 --> 00:11:41,970
[Chaebe: If they're not very expressive,]

269
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:46,990
[Chaebe: I start wondering if they really like me.]

270
00:11:47,650 --> 00:11:50,720
[Chaebe looks lost in thought]

271
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:56,450
[Chaebe: So, the person you like...]

272
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:59,060
[Chaebe: are things going well with them?]

273
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,280
[lost in thought]

274
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:02,800
[Yongkyu: No, not really.]

275
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:05,560
[Yongkyu: Because I haven't made a move.]

276
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:07,840
[Chaebe: They didn't make a move, either?]

277
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,010
[Yongkyu: Yeah, exactly.]

278
00:12:11,110 --> 00:12:13,400
[Chaebe: Are you both just waiting?]

279
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:13,400
-Are you both just waiting? -They probably don't know.

280
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:16,230
[Yongkyu: They probably don't know.]

281
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:19,590
[Yongkyu: If they liked me,]

282
00:12:19,590 --> 00:12:23,050
[Yongkyu: they would've

283
00:12:23,050 --> 00:12:24,300
[Yongkyu: at least talked to me more.]

284
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:26,020
[Yongkyu: But they haven't done anything at all.]

285
00:12:26,020 --> 00:12:27,630
[Then...]

286
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,480
[Yongkyu: I guess I just
don't have enough confidence.]

287
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,160
[Yongkyu: Without confidence, I just...]

288
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:36,070
[Chaebe: But they
might have voted for you, too.]

289
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:40,290
[Chaebe: Why not just take a shot?]

290
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,480
So...

291
00:12:40,290 --> 00:12:43,140
[Yongkyu: I just want things]

292
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:44,460
-Anyway. -to happen naturally.

293
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:45,140
[Yongkyu: to happen naturally?]

294
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:47,810
[Chaebe: It's already day 3.]

295
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:50,100
[Chaebe: There are only about 4 days left.]

296
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:51,350
[Yongkyu: Right.]

297
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:59,830
[Chaebe: I'm really happy
with how things are going.]

298
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:02,630
[Awkward]

299
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,690
[Chaebe: Since I'm here,]

300
00:13:06,690 --> 00:13:10,710
[Chaebe: I want to give it my all
so I have no regrets.]

301
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:15,570
[Chaebe: I used to be so cautious,]

302
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:21,040
[Chaebe: worried that saying the wrong thing]

303
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,720
[Chaebe: might ruin the vibe.]

304
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:24,310
[Chaebe: But that's just not me.]

305
00:13:24,310 --> 00:13:27,760
[Chaebe: I felt so frustrated with myself.]

306
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:38,120
[Chaebe looks upset. Is it because he's nervous?]

307
00:13:38,890 --> 00:13:40,200
[Chaebe: I couldn't see anything at all.]

308
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:42,280
[Yongkyu: Pretend you can see it for the camera.]

309
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,360
[Chaebe: Why don't you take photos
with your phone instead?]

310
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:45,750
-Should I? -Yeah.

311
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:59,540
[Yongkyu: He was a great listener.]

312
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:01,840
[Yongkyu: He can see things
from your perspective when you talk.]

313
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:05,210
[Yongkyu: We actually click really well]

314
00:14:05,210 --> 00:14:06,770
[Yongkyu: in that sense.]

315
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:20,960
[Pottery class wrapped up...]

316
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,830
[Staring]

317
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,630
[Jinwoo: How are you feeling right now?]

318
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:33,650
[Seungho: About what?]

319
00:14:33,650 --> 00:14:36,120
[Jinwoo: After our date.]

320
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,970
[Lost in thought]

321
00:14:39,370 --> 00:14:41,540
[Seungho: I want to explain it clearly,]

322
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,820
[Seungho: but I can't wrap my head around it.]
[Jinwoo: Ah, really?]

323
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,710
[Seungho: First of all, it was super fun.]

324
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:47,210
[Seungho: It was great.]

325
00:14:49,290 --> 00:14:50,020
[Realization]

326
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,260
[Heart thumping]

327
00:14:51,570 --> 00:14:52,330
[Heart thumping]

328
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:57,410
[Jinwoo: You knew I'd pick you today, right?]
[Seungho: Yeah, I knew.]

329
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:57,420
-Yeah, I knew. -I'd pick you for the date.

330
00:14:57,410 --> 00:15:01,660
[Seungho: Yesterday, during the Truth Game,
for the last question...]

331
00:15:01,660 --> 00:15:04,200
[Seungho: you asked me directly.]

332
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:07,270
[Jinwoo: Yeah, but that question
wasn't even hard to answer.]

333
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:10,280
[Jinwoo: You drank instead of answering.]

334
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:14,020
[Seungho: Well...]

335
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,030
[Seungho: It was a bit tough to answer.]

336
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:20,180
[Seungho: Because I didn't know
how you'd take it.]

337
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:23,050
[Jinwoo: We haven't known each other for long.]

338
00:15:23,050 --> 00:15:25,720
[Jinwoo: There are people like me,
and people who are completely different.]

339
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:28,180
[Jinwoo: Spending time with different people]

340
00:15:28,180 --> 00:15:30,630
[Jinwoo: to figure out what you really want—]

341
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:34,100
[Jinwoo: that's the right way to go.]

342
00:15:34,100 --> 00:15:36,310
[Jinwoo: I thought I'd do the same.]

343
00:15:36,310 --> 00:15:37,300
[Jinwoo: I thought I would.]

344
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:39,000
[Jinwoo: But I just can't...]

345
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,170
[Jinwoo: I don't need to...]

346
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:42,540
[Jinwoo: Honestly, I get jealous sometimes.]

347
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,460
[Jinwoo: And sometimes I feel so left out.]

348
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:50,430
[Jinwoo: That's how I see it.]

349
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,200
[Jinwoo: So go ahead and take your time]

350
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,970
[Jinwoo: getting to know other people.]

351
00:15:53,970 --> 00:15:55,600
[Seungho: Seriously?]
[Jinwoo: I'm confident.]

352
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,590
[Seungho: Confident about what?]

353
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:59,960
["You'll end up with me anyway."]

354
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:02,470
[Seungho: Are you serious?]
[Jinwoo: Yeah.]

355
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:05,390
[Seungho: Nice.]

356
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:07,670
[Seungho: I can tell]

357
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,210
[Seungho: he feels strongly about me.]

358
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:12,220
[Seungho: Where does this confidence
even come from?]

359
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:13,710
[Seungho: I'm actually pretty curious.]

360
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:15,250
[Seungho: And I really want to see]

361
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:19,120
[Seungho: what other sides he's going to show me.]

362
00:16:19,930 --> 00:16:21,640
[Seungho: I probably won't date around with everyone.]

363
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:26,140
[Seungho: There is]

364
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:28,300
[Seungho: one more person on my mind.]

365
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:31,730
[Jinwoo: I think I know who it is.]

366
00:16:31,110 --> 00:16:32,210
-Really? -Yeah.

367
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:34,780
[Jinwoo: Honestly, I know.]

368
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:39,350
[Jinwoo: He's torn between me and Hyeyeon.]

369
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:43,740
[Jinwoo: I could feel him

370
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:46,250
[Jinwoo: wavering.]

371
00:16:46,250 --> 00:16:49,310
[Jinwoo: You said your first choice is 60%
and your second is 40%.]

372
00:16:48,450 --> 00:16:49,310
Yeah, exactly.

373
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,180
[Jinwoo: The gap isn't even that big.]

374
00:16:52,690 --> 00:16:56,070
[Jinwoo: Even if I'm second,
I can always catch up to first.]

375
00:16:56,070 --> 00:16:56,840
[Jinwoo: And if I'm first,]

376
00:16:56,840 --> 00:17:00,600
[Jinwoo: I just need to try a bit harder
to pull ahead.]

377
00:17:00,920 --> 00:17:03,510
[Seungho: Do you think you're first? Or second?]

378
00:17:03,510 --> 00:17:04,540
[Jinwoo: Me?]

379
00:17:03,810 --> 00:17:04,480
Yeah.

380
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:07,230
[Jinwoo: I feel like I'm first.]

381
00:17:07,230 --> 00:17:10,530
[Jinwoo: I feel like I'm first.]

382
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:14,310
[Seungho: No comment on that.]

383
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:20,280
[Jinwoo: You don't have to tell me.]

384
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:23,010
[Seungho: Over time,]

385
00:17:23,010 --> 00:17:28,190
[Seungho: things will become clearer, right?]

386
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:33,710
[Seungho: If you like someone else,
go talk to them.]

387
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:34,610
[Seungho: Honestly,]

388
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:36,940
[Seungho: it's better to just
put yourself out there, right?]

389
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:43,880
[Seungho: That way you'll know for sure.]

390
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:48,430
[Jinwoo: You think I have eyes
for someone else, don't you?]

391
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:52,320
[Seungho: You said you did yesterday.]

392
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:53,610
[Jinwoo: But]

393
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,460
[Jinwoo: even if I could]

394
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:58,070
[Jinwoo: choose or decide a date,]

395
00:17:58,070 --> 00:18:01,350
[Jinwoo: I don't like my second choice enough]

396
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:03,210
[Jinwoo: to pick her.]

397
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:06,260
[Seungho: You haven't]

398
00:18:06,260 --> 00:18:08,720
[Seungho: spent any time with her?]

399
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,720
[Jinwoo: Do you know who it is?]
[Seungho: No, so...]

400
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:14,740
[Jinwoo: So you don't know?]

401
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:20,320
[Jinwoo: Actually, at first,]

402
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:23,760
[Jinwoo: Seungho was my number one,
and Hyeyeon was my second.]

403
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:26,150
[Jinwoo: But at some point,]

404
00:18:26,150 --> 00:18:31,590
[Jinwoo: I noticed Hyeyeon
seemed into Seungho, too.]

405
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:33,580
[Jinwoo: It got really confusing.]

406
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:37,450
[Jinwoo: Honestly, right now, I don't even]

407
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:41,840
[Jinwoo: see Hyeyeon as a romantic interest anymore.]

408
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:43,830
[Seungho: You should go put yourself out there.]

409
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:46,800
[Seungho: That's the only way to know for sure.]

410
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,340
[Jinwoo: Right, I need to put myself out there.]

411
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:50,390
[Jinwoo: Date her and see how I actually feel.]

412
00:18:50,390 --> 00:18:51,600
[Jinwoo: But I just don't have those feelings
for her yet.]

413
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:53,360
[Seungho: Really?]
[Jinwoo: Yeah.]

414
00:18:57,020 --> 00:18:59,430
[Jinwoo: Do you feel pressured, Seungho?]

415
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:02,090
[Jinwoo: Am I too...]

416
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:03,840
[Seungho: Not at all. I actually like it.]

417
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:05,640
[Jinwoo: You actually like it?]
[Seungho: Yeah.]

418
00:19:05,910 --> 00:19:08,560
[Jinwoo: I don't want you to walk]

419
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:10,020
[Jinwoo: on eggshells around me.]

420
00:19:11,210 --> 00:19:13,660
[Seungho: Do you think I'm doing that?]

421
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:16,130
[Jinwoo: A little bit?]

422
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:20,300
[Jinwoo: This might sound a bit extreme,]

423
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:25,390
[Jinwoo: but I wondered if you were
doing this out of obligation.]

424
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,830
-Out of obligation. -if you were doing

425
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:24,160
this out of obligation.

426
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:26,700
[Jinwoo: But I could be wrong.]

427
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:30,730
[Jinwoo: Maybe you really mean it.]

428
00:19:28,190 --> 00:19:30,450
-Maybe you really mean it. -Yeah, I do.

429
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:34,590
[Jinwoo: From now on,
I'm just going to do things my way.]

430
00:19:34,910 --> 00:19:38,380
[Jinwoo: You just do things your way, too.]
[Seungho: Okay.]

431
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,200
[Seungho: My way...]

432
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:44,290
[Seungho: I thought Jinwoo at least]

433
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:47,360
[Seungho: had eyes for someone else.]

434
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:51,460
[Seungho: But that day was the first time]

435
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:55,050
[Seungho: I heard him say
I'm the only one on his mind.]

436
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:57,620
[Seungho: That really stuck with me.]

437
00:19:57,620 --> 00:19:59,920
[Jinwoo: Honestly, speaking my mind]

438
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:02,270
[Jinwoo: felt like a massive turning point.]

439
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:05,530
[Jinwoo: I'm so glad we went on this date.]

440
00:20:05,530 --> 00:20:07,250
[Jinwoo: It gives me some peace of mind.]

441
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:13,030
[Time flies by in a blur of butterflies
and jealousy]

442
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:19,660
[Chaebe & Yongkyu continue their date
at a seaside restaurant with a killer view]

443
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,830
[Yongkyu: I'm starving.]

444
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:23,030
[Chaebe: Me too.]

445
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:27,170
[Chaebe: This is going to be so good.]

446
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:33,570
[Mmh.]

447
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,510
[Yongkyu: Do you like burgers?]

448
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,710
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

449
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:44,070
[Chaebe: I don't mind them.]

450
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:45,390
[Yongkyu: Do you eat them often?]

451
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:48,120
[Chaebe: Not lately.]

452
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:52,670
[Chaebe: I'm trying to watch my weight.]

453
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:54,590
[Yongkyu: I absolutely love burgers.]

454
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:58,720
[Yongkyu: Burgers, pizza, fried chicken—
I live for that stuff.]

455
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:02,510
[Chaebe: You love those?]

456
00:21:03,010 --> 00:21:04,270
[Yongkyu: I like Korean food, too,]

457
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:07,290
[Yongkyu: but I definitely have a weak spot
for junk food.]

458
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:09,580
[Chaebe: I'm really into Korean food.]

459
00:21:09,980 --> 00:21:11,300
[Yongkyu: Well, you're Korean.]
[Chaebe: How about gukbap?]

460
00:21:11,390 --> 00:21:12,320
[Gukbap?]

461
00:21:12,320 --> 00:21:13,150
[Gukbap?] [Huh?]

462
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:16,620
[Yongkyu: I have it, too.]

463
00:21:16,620 --> 00:21:17,600
[Mostly?]
[Yongkyu: I have it, too.]

464
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,510
[Mostly?]
[Yongkyu: I just usually pick junk food first.]

465
00:21:20,730 --> 00:21:22,160
[Yongkyu: I love gukbap, too.]

466
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:24,010
[Chaebe: Gukbap is delicious, right?]

467
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:26,920
[Yongkyu: I love gukbap.]
[Chaebe: They're so filling.]

468
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:29,170
[Where did you grow up?]

469
00:21:29,170 --> 00:21:31,260
[Chaebe: Where did I grow up?]

470
00:21:31,260 --> 00:21:32,620
[Chaebe: Actually...]

471
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:34,070
[Chaebe: I lived abroad when I was a kid.]

472
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,020
[Yongkyu: Where?]

473
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:36,680
[Chaebe: I lived abroad as a kid.]
[Yongkyu: Abroad?]

474
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:38,060
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

475
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:40,400
[Yongkyu: Were you born in Korea?]

476
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:42,650
[Chaebe: I was born abroad.]

477
00:21:42,650 --> 00:21:43,990
[Chaebe: Born overseas,]

478
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:46,080
[Chaebe: and moved to Korea during middle school.]

479
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:49,000
[Chaebe: So basically,]

480
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,030
[Chaebe: if you listen closely,]

481
00:21:51,030 --> 00:21:54,270
[Chaebe: my Korean sounds a bit off sometimes.]

482
00:21:54,670 --> 00:21:56,210
[Chaebe: My pronunciation isn't perfect.]

483
00:21:56,210 --> 00:21:57,010
[Chaebe: Can you tell?]

484
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:58,150
[Yongkyu: I thought it was a regional accent.]

485
00:21:58,150 --> 00:22:00,320
[Chaebe: Right? Everyone thinks I have an accent.]

486
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,870
[Chaebe: Nope, it's just because I grew up abroad.]

487
00:22:02,870 --> 00:22:04,700
[Yongkyu: Wow, quite a plot twist.]

488
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,400
[Yongkyu: Is it a secret?]

489
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,310
[Chaebe: No, I can talk about it.]

490
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:08,940
[Chaebe: I used to live in Vietnam.]

491
00:22:08,940 --> 00:22:11,640
[Yongkyu: Ah, so you were born there.]

492
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:14,090
[Chaebe: Yeah, I was born there]

493
00:22:14,090 --> 00:22:17,170
[Chaebe: then moved to Korea in middle school.]

494
00:22:17,170 --> 00:22:18,700
[Yongkyu: Did you move back for good?]

495
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:19,640
[Chaebe: Yeah, I'm fully settled in Korea now.]

496
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:22,880
[Yongkyu: What about your citizenship?]
[Chaebe: I'm a Korean citizen, of course.]

497
00:22:24,360 --> 00:22:26,800
[Chaebe: I like him,]

498
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:28,620
[Chaebe: so why should I hide anything?]

499
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:30,890
[Chaebe: I want him to know]

500
00:22:30,890 --> 00:22:34,180
[Chaebe: who I really am.]

501
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:38,100
[Chaebe: So I just told him.]

502
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:41,140
[Yongkyu: Vietnam was unexpected.]

503
00:22:41,140 --> 00:22:42,320
[Is it?] [Yeah.]

504
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,160
[Yongkyu: Vietnam...]

505
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,340
[Yongkyu: Where in Vietnam?]

506
00:22:44,340 --> 00:22:45,700
[Ho Chi Minh.]

507
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:46,890
[Ho Chi Minh.] [Ho Chi Minh.]

508
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:49,890
[Yongkyu: Of course, I know it. I know Hanoi too.]

509
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:49,890
Have you been?

510
00:22:49,890 --> 00:22:50,990
[Yongkyu: And Da Nang.]

511
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,720
[Chaebe: Have you been there?]
[Yongkyu: No, never.]

512
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:54,250
[Yongkyu: I really want to go, though.]

513
00:22:54,250 --> 00:22:55,900
[Yongkyu: How long is the flight? 5 hours?]

514
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:57,390
[Yeah.]
[Yongkyu: How long is the flight? 5 hours?]

515
00:22:57,740 --> 00:23:00,230
[Yongkyu: Honestly, your Korean
is practically native level.]

516
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:02,380
[Yongkyu: Your Korean is perfect.]
[Chaebe: Well, I am a Korean citizen.]

517
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:03,240
[Chaebe: I am Korean, after all.]

518
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:08,450
[Yongkyu: Nobody would ever question it.]

519
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:11,750
[Yongkyu: I bet your Vietnamese is perfect, too.]

520
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:13,880
[Chaebe: Yeah, totally.]

521
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:18,710
[Opening up to someone he likes]

522
00:23:18,710 --> 00:23:20,970
[Chaebe: Do you text back fast, or...]

523
00:23:20,970 --> 00:23:22,460
[Yongkyu: Me?]

524
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:24,320
[Yongkyu: Mmh... I text back fast.]

525
00:23:24,320 --> 00:23:26,950
[Chaebe: Do you like it when the other person
texts back fast, or...]

526
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,860
[like you mentioned earlier—] [The other person?]

527
00:23:28,860 --> 00:23:31,140
[Chaebe: someone who's a little more like a cat—]

528
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:32,400
[Chaebe: showing up when they feel like it.]

529
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,670
[Yongkyu: Well, I feel like]

530
00:23:33,670 --> 00:23:36,180
[Yongkyu: during work hours, we'd just
text things like "Have a good day at work"]

531
00:23:36,180 --> 00:23:37,630
[Yongkyu: or "Have you eaten?"]

532
00:23:37,630 --> 00:23:40,050
[Yongkyu: and maybe chat a little in between.]

533
00:23:40,050 --> 00:23:41,480
[Yongkyu: It's not like we can reply instantly
all the time when we're busy.]

534
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,710
[Yongkyu: We can just talk]

535
00:23:42,710 --> 00:23:44,560
[Yongkyu: whenever we're free.]

536
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,270
[Yongkyu: That's probably how it would be.]

537
00:23:46,930 --> 00:23:49,070
[Yongkyu: What about you? How do you text?]

538
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:51,300
[Chaebe: I love texting.]

539
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,380
[Yongkyu: Do you reply instantly?]

540
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:55,030
[Chaebe: Yeah, almost always.]

541
00:23:55,470 --> 00:23:58,190
[Yongkyu: But do you]

542
00:23:58,190 --> 00:23:59,960
[Yongkyu: wait a bit to reply?]

543
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:02,180
[Yongkyu: Playing hard to get?]

544
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:04,660
[Chaebe: No, I never play hard to get.]

545
00:24:04,660 --> 00:24:06,060
[Chaebe: Do you?]

546
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:07,960
[Yongkyu: I wouldn't say I like it.]

547
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:10,020
[Yongkyu: It just happens sometimes,]

548
00:24:10,020 --> 00:24:11,960
[Yongkyu: not even on purpose, you know.]

549
00:24:12,930 --> 00:24:14,530
[Yongkyu: You remember
your first text to me, right?]

550
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:15,350
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

551
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:20,600
[Yongkyu: I took a while to reply, didn't I?]

552
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,820
[Yongkyu: I took a while to reply, didn't I?]

553
00:24:21,820 --> 00:24:24,330
[Chaebe: But we only get 7 texts]

554
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:25,940
[Chaebe: here anyway.]

555
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:28,930
[Chaebe: I just figured you were]

556
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:31,390
[Chaebe: thinking carefully before replying.]

557
00:24:31,390 --> 00:24:32,560
[Chaebe: And]

558
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:37,300
[Chaebe: we had to text the person
we're interested in,]

559
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:41,050
[Chaebe: so I just texted you,]

560
00:24:41,990 --> 00:24:43,760
[Chaebe: even though I was worried]

561
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,060
[Chaebe: you might not reply.]

562
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,930
[Yongkyu: Well,]

563
00:24:46,930 --> 00:24:50,250
[Yongkyu: your text was like,
"Thanks for the food".]

564
00:24:50,250 --> 00:24:52,050
[Yongkyu: I didn't read into it.]

565
00:24:52,050 --> 00:24:55,290
[Yongkyu: I literally just thought you
enjoyed the meal.]

566
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:57,190
[Yongkyu: Am I really that clueless?]

567
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,790
[Oh boy...]

568
00:24:59,210 --> 00:25:00,780
[Chaebe: No, it's not like that.]

569
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:04,300
[Chaebe: The way I expressed it was a little...]
[Yongkyu: That's honestly all I meant.]

570
00:25:04,950 --> 00:25:07,910
[Chaebe: I kept overthinking]

571
00:25:07,910 --> 00:25:10,750
[Chaebe: what I should say.]

572
00:25:11,490 --> 00:25:13,760
[Chaebe: It really was delicious, though...]

573
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,590
[Yongkyu: I thought you just genuinely
liked the food.]

574
00:25:15,590 --> 00:25:17,990
[Yongkyu: All I thought was,]

575
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,110
[Yongkyu: "I'll cook for you again if you want."]

576
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:22,640
[Chaebe: Still, I was so happy you replied.]

577
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:25,710
[Yongkyu: And then we fell out of touch, right?]

578
00:25:26,780 --> 00:25:29,330
[Chaebe: I wanted to keep texting you,
but...]

579
00:25:29,860 --> 00:25:31,210
[Yongkyu: Ah, did you dodge me on purpose?]

580
00:25:31,210 --> 00:25:33,070
[Chaebe: I just felt like...]

581
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:36,550
[Chaebe: you might not like it.]
[Yongkyu: Ah, you wanted to take it slow?]

582
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:38,340
[Chaebe: So I just...]

583
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,960
[Chaebe: I still]

584
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,540
[Chaebe: wanted to be careful—]

585
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:43,410
[Mmh.]
[Chaebe: only saying what really mattered.]

586
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:50,630
[Discovering the true meaning
behind Chaebe's first text]

587
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:47,010
And, about texting...

588
00:25:50,930 --> 00:25:53,330
[Chaebe: we're always together.]

589
00:25:53,330 --> 00:25:55,260
[Chaebe: All of us.]
[Yongkyu: Yeah. Ah, right.]

590
00:25:55,260 --> 00:25:57,760
[Chaebe: So when we text, I just want]

591
00:25:57,760 --> 00:26:00,700
[Chaebe: to just say what I really want to say.]

592
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:02,710
[Yongkyu: How did it feel being
at the house yesterday?]

593
00:26:02,710 --> 00:26:03,680
[Yongkyu: Was it fun?]

594
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:05,280
[Yongkyu: Yesterday, when the 4
of us were at the house...]

595
00:26:04,170 --> 00:26:06,170
-Yesterday? -When the 4 of us were at the house...

596
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:10,490
[Chaebe: I loved that we stayed together.]

597
00:26:10,690 --> 00:26:12,110
[Chaebe: But being stuck inside]

598
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:15,440
[Chaebe: was a bit of a bummer.]

599
00:26:14,410 --> 00:26:15,270
Yeah, totally.

600
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:19,880
[Chaebe: Plus, we didn't get any time to talk]

601
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:22,000
[Chaebe: one-on-one.]

602
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:27,410
[Yongkyu: So, are you happy with our date today?]

603
00:26:27,410 --> 00:26:28,960
[Chaebe: I'm really happy.]

604
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,640
[Yeah, me too.]

605
00:26:30,830 --> 00:26:32,240
-So happy, seriously. -I...

606
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:34,480
[Chaebe: I...]

607
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,410
[Chaebe: give it a perfect score.]

608
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:36,310
[A perfect score?]

609
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,160
[Yep, haha.] [A perfect score?]

610
00:26:39,910 --> 00:26:41,680
[Chaebe: I'm so content.]

611
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:43,690
[Chaebe: I could literally go home right now.]

612
00:26:46,890 --> 00:26:53,830
[Chaebe: At the house, we're always in a crowd.]

613
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:58,870
[Chaebe: We never get to talk one-on-one like this.]

614
00:26:58,870 --> 00:27:01,200
[Chaebe: I was just really happy]

615
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:04,410
[Chaebe: coming out together]

616
00:27:04,410 --> 00:27:07,880
[Chaebe: and talking just the two of us.]

617
00:27:09,610 --> 00:27:12,320
[Yongkyu: I have a better idea]

618
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:15,180
[Yongkyu: of how he feels about me now.]

619
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:18,400
[Yongkyu: That brought us closer.]

620
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:21,460
[Yongkyu: Hanging out with him was so much fun.]

621
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:23,870
[Yongkyu: He was completely honest]

622
00:27:23,870 --> 00:27:25,960
[Yongkyu: with me, too.]

623
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:28,950
[Yongkyu: I really liked that about him.]

624
00:27:30,670 --> 00:27:38,850
[Where will their relationship go after this date?]

625
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:41,040
Who knows how things will change?

626
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:43,210
[A phone suddenly buzzes]

627
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:41,960
I have no idea.

628
00:27:45,850 --> 00:27:47,930
[Jinwoo: Wait, did you hear something just now?]

629
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,750
[Seungho: Maybe I should check it.]

630
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,590
No clue.

631
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:59,820
[Hyeyeon: How was the date? I'm back at the beach.
I'll tell you everything later.]

632
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,080
Is it spam?

633
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:02,970
[Seungho receives Hyeyeon's SBM Talk]

634
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:05,230
[Jinwoo: You didn't get a text, did you?]

635
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:08,300
[Seungho: I got an SBM Talk.]
[Jinwoo: Oh, really?]

636
00:28:07,450 --> 00:28:08,230
Yeah.

637
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:10,710
[Seungho: But we're on a date.]

638
00:28:10,710 --> 00:28:13,270
[Seungho: I'll reply later.]

639
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:15,290
[Jinwoo: What did they say?]

640
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:18,800
[Seungho: Someone at the beach texted me.]

641
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:21,040
[Jinwoo: Oh, someone at the beach texted you?]

642
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:22,330
[Seungho: Yeah.]

643
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:29,160
[Seungho: One pair went to the beach.]

644
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:34,270
[Jinwoo: The beach pair...]

645
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:36,870
[Seungho: I got a text from Hyeyeon.]

646
00:28:36,870 --> 00:28:39,650
[Seungho: I figured it was better
to reply after the date ended.]

647
00:28:39,650 --> 00:28:41,210
[Seungho: So on the drive back,]

648
00:28:41,210 --> 00:28:43,270
[Seungho: I texted her back.]

649
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:50,100
[Seungho: Oh, the beach. I did some pottery, haha.
Heading back to the house now.
I'll fill you in later, too.]

650
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:52,910
[Jinwoo: Did you reply to that SBM Talk?]

651
00:28:52,910 --> 00:28:54,980
[Seungho: I just did.]

652
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:54,770
-I just did. -Just now?

653
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:56,360
[Seungho: Curious?]

654
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:59,560
[Jinwoo: What do you think]

655
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:02,190
[Jinwoo: when you read it?]

656
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:05,140
[Seungho: Hold on.]

657
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:07,040
[Seungho: What do I think?]

658
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,180
[Smirking]

659
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:10,830
[Seungho: Instead of trying to hide it from him,]

660
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:13,140
[Seungho: I actually wanted to show him.]

661
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:15,240
[Seungho: Like, look, I got a text!]

662
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:16,790
[Seungho: To make him jealous?]

663
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,620
[Seungho: Going to the beach twice?]

664
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:26,210
[The person who went
to the beach twice texted Seungho]

665
00:29:26,550 --> 00:29:27,960
[Jinwoo: Now I'm curious...]

666
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,360
[Jinwoo: Never mind, I don't care anymore.]

667
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:30,280
[Seungho: About what?]

668
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,850
[Jinwoo: Who sent it.]

669
00:29:32,850 --> 00:29:34,550
[Jinwoo: I have a pretty good feeling
I know who it is.]
[Seungho: Really?]

670
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:37,050
[Jinwoo: But I'm actually relieved.]

671
00:29:37,050 --> 00:29:38,610
[Jinwoo: Because it was her.]

672
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,900
[Seungho: Because it wasn't someone else?]

673
00:29:40,900 --> 00:29:45,820
[Jinwoo: If anyone else felt that way too,]

674
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:48,140
[Jinwoo: I'd have way too much to worry about.]

675
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:51,320
[Jinwoo: Since it's exactly who I expected,]

676
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:53,700
[Jinwoo: I can relax a bit.]

677
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:58,180
[Seungho: He expressed his feelings for me]

678
00:29:58,180 --> 00:30:00,610
[Seungho: so clearly.]

679
00:30:00,610 --> 00:30:05,000
[Seungho: That really stood out to me.]

680
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:10,050
[The feelings of these 8 singles are growing deeper]

681
00:30:10,580 --> 00:30:13,910
[Sujin: Do you think anyone's inside?]
[Heejin: I think we're the first ones back.]

682
00:30:14,650 --> 00:30:18,280
[Sujin & Heejin arrive first at the house]

683
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:15,600
Oh man.

684
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:22,450
[The house is completely quiet for a change]

685
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,460
So hot.

686
00:30:23,180 --> 00:30:24,010
Let's go.

687
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:28,900
[Heejin: I'm heading up. See you in a bit.]
[Sujin: Okay.]

688
00:30:32,290 --> 00:30:34,670
[Exhausted]

689
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:39,440
[Heejin: I just wanted to change]

690
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,670
[Heejin: and collapse into bed.]

691
00:30:40,670 --> 00:30:43,050
[Heejin: I felt completely drained.]

692
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:46,990
[Crashing onto the bed from sudden exhaustion]

693
00:30:52,010 --> 00:30:55,710
[Meanwhile, Hyeyeon & Eunchae arrive]

694
00:30:57,360 --> 00:31:01,200
[Eunchae: I'll wash my feet first.]
[Hyeyeon: Catch you later if we get a chance.]

695
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:04,080
[Eunchae: See you in a bit.]
[Hyeyeon: Okay.]

696
00:31:09,330 --> 00:31:13,890
[Dropping her bag, Hyeyeon heads back to the annex]

697
00:31:20,370 --> 00:31:24,120
[Hey, Sujin.]

698
00:31:24,320 --> 00:31:25,590
[Sujin: Is the door locked?]

699
00:31:25,590 --> 00:31:28,010
[Hyeyeon: Can I come in?]

700
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,000
Yeah, go ahead.

701
00:31:28,010 --> 00:31:31,480
[Sujin: Hyeyeon, when did you get back?]
[Hyeyeon: Just now.]

702
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:31,520
